about_doc_info:
About Prof. Dr. Javed Iqbal
Bio
Prof. Dr. Javed Iqbal is a highly qualified Laparoscopic surgeon in Bahawalpur with over 3 decades of experience. He is currently a Professor of Surgery and Director DME and Quaid-e- Azam Medical College. He claims that medical education is his second love as he is also a published poet and also writes Urdu prose. He has a YouTube channel where he promotes education and uploads motivational videos.
Qualifications
Prof. Dr. Javed Iqbal finished his MBBS from Nishter Medical College in Multan. He then completed his FCPS (Surgery) from College of Physicians of Surgeon and his FCPS (Surgery) from the Royal College of Surgeons in Glasgow. He then perfected his qualifications by completing his MCPS (Surgery) from HPE.
Experience
Prof. Dr. Javed Iqbal has over 35 years of experience as a Laparoscopic surgeon. He is currently a Professor of Surgery at and Director DME at Quaid-e-Azam Medical College and was previously the Principal here as well.
Activism
Prof. Dr. Javed Iqbal has a YouTube channel where he likes to raise awareness on the benefits of education and he also uploads motivational videos. He speaks about familial and societal issues in his videos. In a video he spoke about the second wave of Coronavirus is spreading across the world and in Pakistan as well. He mentioned how the second wave of the virus was due to a couple of factors, such as the natural course of the virus as well as the public getting too relaxed with SOPs. He also urged viewers to follow SOPs and to always wear a mask and sanitize and to avoid crowded areas.
Special Interests
Prof. Dr. Javed Iqbal has a special interest in poetry and is a published poet. He also has an interest in Laparoscopic and endocrine surgery.
Contact Details
In order to book an appointment with Prof. Dr. Javed Iqbal you can call 0618048444  or click the book appointment button on the right side of the page.

About Prof. Dr. Ghulam Mujtaba
Bio
Prof. Dr. Ghulam Mujtaba is a veteran in the field of dermatology, often regarded as one of the best Dermatologists in Pakistan. Being an experienced professional, he is extremely competent in dealing with a wide range of services such as Skin Care Consultation, Procedural Dermatology, Melasma, Dermal Fillers, Cryotherapy & Electrocautery For Removal Of Warts, Chemical Peel, Antihistamine Treatment, Alopecia & Acne Treatment etc Dr. Ghulam Mujtaba is a seasoned skincare expert who has treated a huge number of cases over many years and is well respected for his professionalism & the ability to handle minor & major dermatological issues & concerns with extreme care.
Qualifications
Prof. Dr. Ghulam Mujtaba is an M.B.B.S with a Fellowship in the College of Physicians & Surgeons Pakistan. He is a highly qualified dermatologist with extensive knowledge & understanding of the conventional as well as the latest trends in cosmetology procedures and this unique blend of education & expertise has enabled him to be a master of his craft while continuing to excel in the field of dermatology.
Experience
When it comes to experience, there are not many people with such a decorated profile as Dr. Ghulam. He has vast amounts of experience ranging over 33 years and is currently practicing as a Consultant Dermatologist & Cosmetologist at Skin Care Clinic, Khan Medical City Hospital, Multan & Council Member of the College of Physicians & Surgeons, Pakistan. Dr. Ghulam Mujtaba is a PMDC Registered Medical Professional who has been serving in the field for more than three decades and continues to serve the community with his expert insight & exceptional quality of work.
Activism
Prof. Ghulam Mujtaba has a proactive approach when it comes to raising awareness to the masses and has taken over several roles in order to attain this goal. He is an accomplished researcher, writer & public speaker who attends numerous conferences both in & out of the country and stays up to date with the latest advancements in dermatology practices. He is one of the most experienced skin specialists in Pakistan who has been extremely active on several platforms and continues to raise his voice on every available forum to share factual information related to skin & hair care issues. Dr. Ghulam is a part of various health seminars & public speaking sessions as he is extremely devoted in the pursuit of spreading awareness for the general population and is one of the pioneers when it comes to the Introduction & development of globally recognized dermatology standards in Pakistan.
Special Interests
Dr. Ghulam Mujtaba is a proficient dermatologist with the capabilities to deal with a diverse range of services but his main area of interest lies in specialized dermatology treatments including Hair Fall Treatment, Nails Treatment, Laser for Acne, Skin Rejuvenation, Stretch marks removal & Other Skin Issues, Dr. Ghulam takes great pride in his work and his accomplishments as a skin specialist operating in the field for more than thirty years, make him one of the most well-reputed figures providing skincare consultation in Pakistan.
